Package: portR
Title: Build Portable R Application Distributions
Version: 0.2.0
Authors@R:
    person("Alessandro", "Gerada", , "alessandro.gerada@liverpool.ac.uk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Build portable distributions of R Shiny applications that can
    run without requiring R installation on the target machine. Supports
    building for Windows (with .bat launcher) and macOS (with shell script
    launcher). Uses renv lockfiles to determine package dependencies and
    downloads binary packages from CRAN.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.3
Imports:
    jsonlite
Suggests:
    testthat (>= 3.0.0)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
